Dumpster - Recover Deleted Photos & Video Recovery

Brief: Dumpster is an indispensable recovery tool for Android users, providing a safety net for those moments when you accidentally delete a file or photo you didn't mean to. Acting as a digital recycle bin, it grants you the power to restore deleted items with ease. Offering both a free service and a premium cloud-based solution, Dumpster simplifies the process of data recovery while assisting in freeing up storage space on your device.
